OL,3,CTown's parasite outbreak cost water
OL,4,Ccompany millions
OL,6,FThe owner of South West Water (SWW)
OL,7,Fhas said a parasite outbreak in the
OL,8,Fwater supply in Devon earlier this
OL,9,Fyear cost it #16.3million, pushing it
OL,10,Ffurther into the red in the first half
OL,11,Fof the financial year.
OL,13,FThe Pennon Group said it had to pay
OL,14,Fout compensation to affected customers
OL,15,Fafter the cryptosporidium outbreak in
OL,16,FBrixham, south Devon, which left some
OL,17,Fpeople in hospital with more than 100
OL,18,Fothers reporting symptoms.
