OL,6,FIt said the #16.3million went towards
OL,7,Fproviding eight weeks' worth of
OL,8,Fbottled water for people in the
OL,9,Faffected area, carrying out "extensive
OL,10,Finterventions to clean and filter the
OL,11,Fnetwork" and compensating customers.
OL,13,FChief executive Susan Davy said: "When
OL,14,Fthings go wrong, as they did for
OL,15,Fcustomers and businesses in and around
OL,16,FBrixham earlier this year, we put it
OL,17,Fright, with no excuses. But we know we
OL,18,Fhave more to do."
