OL,6,FThe Pennon Group said it made a
OL,7,F#38.8million pre-tax loss in the six
OL,8,Fmonths to September.
OL,10,FCapital spending, on things like
OL,11,Fupgrading its water infrastructure,
OL,12,Frose to #331.8million, up about a
OL,13,Fquarter on the same period last year.
OL,15,FWater firms have drawn public outrage
OL,16,Fin recent years over the extent of
OL,17,Fpollution and other incidents, amid
OL,18,Fsteep planned increases to bills, high
OL,19,Fdividends, and executive pay and
OL,20,Fbonuses.
