OL,6,FPennon has asked regulators to let it
OL,7,Fincrease average consumer bills at
OL,8,FSouth West Water by 23% over the next
OL,9,Ffive years, with Ofwat's final
OL,10,Fdecision due in December.
OL,12,FSouth West Water also launched an
OL,13,Fawareness campaign in February aimed
OL,14,Fat getting customers to use less
OL,15,Fwater, which also hit first-half
OL,16,Frevenues.
OL,18,FMs Davy added: "We continue to lead
OL,19,Fthe way in helping customers to use
OL,20,Fless and save more with a range of
OL,21,Fmoney-saving campaigns and pilots.
